00:06:55.000 --> 00:07:07.000
So while this is booting up, before we do any analyses, it's really important that we establish a new RStudio project for this clinical trial analysis.

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:13.000
So this will provide us with a working directory for this project and only this project.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:20.000
So this helps ensure that the analyses we do here, that they won't impact anything else on our system or another project.

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:27.000
And this is generally considered good practice for not just clinical trial data, but really all data science projects.

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:32.000
So to create a project, we have a few different options.

00:07:32.000 --> 00:07:35.000
