00:08:02.000 --> 00:08:04.000
So we're going to go ahead and create a new directory.

00:08:05.000 --> 00:08:10.000
But I do have a choice to create a project within an existing directory or pull in a project from Version Control.

00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:12.000
But we'll stick with New Directory.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:15.000
Select New Project, the first option.

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:22.000
