00:08:41.000 --> 00:08:45.000
So while this is booting up, a quick note on those two boxes that we just checked.

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:52.000
So to ensure reproducibility for your project, it's always a good idea to use Version Control

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:56.000
and to initialize the project with something known as renv.

00:08:56.000 --> 00:09:02.000
Now once we finish our workflow today, we'll actually go back and discuss renv in more detail

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:07.000
